> ## Distributed Memory Example
>
> Create a new script called `mpi.sl`
>
> ```
> #!/bin/bash -e
> 
> #SBATCH --name            MPI-job
> #SBATCH --output          %x.out
> #SBATCH --mem-per-cpu     500
> #SBATCH --ntasks          4
> 
> srun bash whothis.sh
> ```
> {: .language-bash}
> 
> then submit with 
> 
> ```
> {{ site.remote.prompt }} sbatch mpi.sl
> ```
